=== 正面評價 ===
針對舆论的批評，導演郭敬明亦作出回應，否認《小时代》“拜金”，並回擊著名影評人[[周黎明|周黎明]]“你看見什麼你就是什麼”<ref>{{cite news | title=郭敬明暗讽周黎明没看懂？ | url=http://ent.ifeng.com/HOT/yaowen/detail_2013_06/29/26943750_0.shtml | publisher=[[凤凰网|凤凰网]] | date=2013-06-29 | accessdate=2013-07-05 | archive-date=2019-09-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905082747/http://ent.ifeng.com/HOT/yaowen/detail_2013_06/29/26943750_0.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>。不少評論認為，《小时代》引起争议的原因在於不同年齡段之間的代溝<ref>{{cite news | title=The generation gap - Living large | url=http://www.economist.com/blogs/analects/2013/07/generation-gap | publisher=经济学人 | date=2013-07-17 | accessdate=2013-07-27 | archive-date=2015-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924005704/http://www.economist.com/blogs/analects/2013/07/generation-gap | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=吴虹飞：代沟令史航老人家跟郭粉争论很正常 | url=http://ent.ifeng.com/movie/special/xiaoshidai/content-3/detail_2013_07/04/27143842_0.shtml | publisher=凤凰网 | date=2013-07-04 | accessdate=2013-07-05 | archive-date=2020-08-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813210229/http://ent.ifeng.com/movie/special/xiaoshidai/content-3/detail_2013_07/04/27143842_0.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>，僅僅一部電影也不至於改變年輕人的價值觀，將批評矛頭指向人生觀、價值觀是“上綱上線”<ref>{{cite news | title=《小时代》，真能绑架价值观？ | url=http://news.xhby.net/system/2013/07/18/017979312.shtml | publisher=新华报业网 | date=2013-07-18 | access-date=2013-07-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714203448/http://news.xhby.net/system/2013/07/18/017979312.shtml | archive-date=2014-07-14 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=“小时代”是心理高手 | url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2013-07-27/023927783356.shtml | publisher=新浪 | date=2013-07-27 | accessdate=2013-07-27 | archive-date=2019-08-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811045337/http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2013-07-27/023927783356.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>。亦有評論認為《小時代》定位精準、受眾清晰，成功挖掘出了青少年觀影市場，是一部值得借鑒的國產類型片<ref>{{cite news | title=人民日报：我们的电影让青少年“饥饿”了太久 | url=http://ent.ifeng.com/movie/special/xiaoshidai/content-3/detail_2013_07/02/27020874_0.shtml | publisher=凤凰网 | date=2013-07-02 | accessdate=2013-07-05 | archive-date=2020-08-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813192854/http://ent.ifeng.com/movie/special/xiaoshidai/content-3/detail_2013_07/02/27020874_0.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=央视力挺《小时代》系列：精准营销才是成功关键 | url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20130801/017421.htm | publisher=腾讯网 | date=2013-08-01 | accessdate=2013-08-01 | archive-date=2019-11-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129094631/https://ent.qq.com/a/20130801/017421.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《[[小时代：青木时代|小时代2]]》上映的第二天，之前批評小时代的《人民日报》改口风，《人民日报》海外版发文《整顿世风不能靠打压<小时代>》写到：整顿世风、收拾人心，不能靠打压郭敬明之类的作品，就好像振兴传统文化不能靠[[于丹|于丹]]一样<ref>{{cite web | url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2013-08-09/14073984127.shtml | title=《人民日报》改口风：不能打压《小时代》 | publisher=新浪娱乐 | work= | date=2013-08-09 | accessdate=2013-08-09 | archive-date=2019-08-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813145552/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2013-08-09/14073984127.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://opinion.haiwainet.cn/n/2013/0809/c232601-19273103.html | title=熊建：整顿世风不能靠打压《小时代》 | publisher=海外网 | work=人民日报海外版 | date=2013-08-09 | accessdate=2013-08-09 | archive-date=2013-11-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104123818/http://opinion.haiwainet.cn/n/2013/0809/c232601-19273103.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

